title: Project 1
text:
The response is the length of odontoblasts in 60 guinea pigs. Each animal received one of three dose levels of vitamin C (0.5, 1 and 2 mg/day) by one of two delivery methods, orange juice or ascorbic acid (a form of vitamin C and coded as VC).
The first 3 observations of the dataset:

head(ToothGrowth, 3)

   len supp dose
1  4.2   VC  0.5
2 11.5   VC  0.5
3  7.3   VC  0.5


A box plot:

library(tidyverse)

ToothGrowth |>
  mutate(dose = as.factor(dose)) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = dose, y = len, fill = dose)) +
  geom_boxplot()
